JP-009 complete. Committed `fcaef41`.

**Summary of what was built:**
- 12 new functions in `host.js` for the buzzing → judging → score pipeline
- `onOpenBuzzing` writes Firebase buzzer state, starts countdown timer, listens for player buzzes
